== 系列影响 ==
模拟人生系列的成功使得其多项成绩被[[吉尼斯世界纪录|吉尼斯世界纪录]]授予认证，这其中就包括截至2017年的“最多视频游戏系列资料片（{{lang|en|Most Expansion Packs for a Videogame Series}}）”及“最畅销电脑游戏系列（{{lang|en|Best Selling PC Game Series}}）”。据估计，模拟人生系列的销售量在3600万到5000万份之间<ref>{{cite book |author1=[[吉尼斯世界纪录|吉尼斯世界纪录]] |title=Guinness World Records 2017 Gamer's Edition |date=2016-08-30 |publisher=Guinness World Records |isbn=9781910561416 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=MNEyDQAAQBAJ |page=169 |accessdate=2020-03-26}}</ref>。截至2019年10月，模拟人生系列所有游戏的累积总销售额超过了50亿[[美元|美元]]<ref>{{cite web |author1=Rebekah Valentine |title=The Sims franchise surpasses $5b in lifetime sales |url=https://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/2019-10-29-the-sims-franchise-surpasses-usd5b-in-lifetime-sales |publisher=GamesIndustry.biz |accessdate=2020-03-26 |archive-date=2019-10-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191030104034/https://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/2019-10-29-the-sims-franchise-surpasses-usd5b-in-lifetime-sales |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 改编计划 ===
根据模拟人生系列游戏改编的[[真人电影|真人]][[劇情片|剧情电影]]曾宣布在2007年上映<ref>{{cite web |title=The Sims Coming to the Big Screen |url=https://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/20635-the-sims-coming-to-the-big-screen |website=ComingSoon.net |publisher=[[综艺_(杂志)|综艺]] |accessdate=2020-03-26 |archive-date=2014-10-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141019112838/http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=20635 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2007年5月25日，模拟人生系列的电影改编权被宣布被[[20世纪福斯电影公司|20世纪福斯公司]]收购<ref>{{cite web |title="The Sims" to move from PC screen to silver screen |url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-electronicarts-thesims/the-sims-to-move-from-pc-screen-to-silver-screen-idUSN2519868120070528 |publisher=[[路透社|路透社]] |accessdate=2020-03-26 |archive-date=2020-02-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200226165245/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-electronicarts-thesims/the-sims-to-move-from-pc-screen-to-silver-screen-idUSN2519868120070528 |dead-url=no }}</ref>；这部电影计划由{{Link-en|布莱恩·林奇|Brian Lynch (writer)}}担任编剧，而由{{Link-en|约翰·戴维斯 (制片人)|John Davis (producer)|约翰·戴维斯}}担任制片<ref>{{cite web |author1=Steve 'Frosty' Weintraub |title=Producer John Davis Gives Updates on THE SIMS Movie, the Aliens vs. Predator Movies and Jason and the Argonauts! |url=https://collider.com/producer-john-davis-gives-updates-on-the-sims-movie-the-aliens-vs-predator-movies-and-jason-and-the-argonauts/ |publisher=[[Collider|Collider]] |accessdate=2020-03-26 |archive-date=2020-09-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200919102201/https://collider.com/producer-john-davis-gives-updates-on-the-sims-movie-the-aliens-vs-predator-movies-and-jason-and-the-argonauts/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author1=Emma Boyes |title=The Sims movie planned |url=http://www.gamespot.com/articles/the-sims-movie-planned/1100-6171544/ |publisher=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]] |accessdate=2020-03-26 |archive-date=2020-03-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200326083633/https://www.gamespot.com/articles/the-sims-movie-planned/1100-6171544/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。但是在2019年，由[[迪士尼收購21世紀福斯|华特迪士尼公司收购21世纪福斯公司]]之后，该电影及其他20世纪福斯电影公司正在开发的诸多基于游戏改编的电影都被宣布取消<ref>{{cite web |author1=Eric Switzer |title=Disney Just Scrapped Mega Man, Magic: The Gathering, And Sims Movies |url=https://www.thegamer.com/disney-cancels-mega-man-magic-the-gathering-fox-merger/ |publisher=TheGamer |accessdate=2020-03-26 |archive-date=2020-11-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201107234920/https://www.thegamer.com/disney-cancels-mega-man-magic-the-gathering-fox-merger/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 衍生遊戲 ===
模拟人生系列作為[[生活模擬遊戲|生活模擬遊戲]]，啟發開發者參考改編為[[另類實境遊戲|另類實境遊戲]]。其中類似的包括由京都大學學生負責開發的[[惡用禁止人生遊戲|惡用禁止人生遊戲]]，該遊戲參考模拟人生系列，並把遊戲內容融入現實的世界及真實的情境。<ref>{{Cite web|title=悪用禁止人生ゲーム {{!}} 公式サイト {{!}} 惡用禁止人生遊戲|url=https://www.lifegamejapan.com/|accessdate=2020-08-13|work=悪用禁止人生ゲーム公式サイト|language=ja|archive-date=2020-09-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200903023427/https://www.lifegamejapan.com/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

